column1: CalSim II ROC on LTO COS
column3: CalSim II Current Operations Study (COS) from the Reinitiation of Consulation on the Coordinated Long-Term Operations (ROC on LTO) of the Central Valley Project (CVP) and the State Water Project (SWP) Draft Environmental Impact Statement. The Current Operations Scenario represents CVP and SWP operations to comply with the "current" regulatory environment (as of December 27, 2017) under projected Year 2030 conditions.
column5: Model run assumptions are described in Section 3.1 of Appendix D of the ROC on LTO Draft EIS, available at https://cdxnodengn.epa.gov/cdx-enepa-II/public/action/eis/details?eisId=276781
